{"word":"ἀγρυπνέω","slug":"ἀγρυπνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγρυπνέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγρυπνος'><el>ἄγρυπνος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to lie awake, be wakeful</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>; <el>ἀγρυπνεῖν τὴν νύκτα</el> <i>to pass a sleepless</i> night, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to be watchful</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}